Azure AI: https://language.cognitive.azure.com/tryout/sentiment
API Documentation: https://pypi.org/project/azure-ai-textanalytics/#analyze-sentiment
Azure AI Language includes four main functions: sentiment analysis, key phrase extraction, language detection, and named entity recognition.

Capabilities of Microsoft Azure AI Language Studio: 
1. Language detection - sentiment analysis, opinion mining
2. Extract named entities
3. Extract PII 
4. Extract key phrases 
